- Items can be created.
- All items can be filtered with various variables
- Items can then be added to DRAFT lists.

- Grocery lists will stay in DRAFT until user moves them to another.
- Grocery lists can be given unique names.

- User can create grocery lists
 - Should be able to drag historical items onto lists
 - Should be able to move list to certain statuses:
    - DRAFT: a ready to shop list
    - SHOPPING: items can be removed to simulate shopping.
    - COMPLETED: all items on the list are purchased.
    - ITEMS_PENDING: items not found on list.

- Items outstanding in other lists will be notified to users.
